<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<%- include('../partials/head.ejs') %>

<style>
  .payment-card {
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: none;
  }

  .payment-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .payment-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6c757d;
  }

  .qr-box {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .qr-placeholder {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 15px;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
  }

  .qr-placeholder i {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .qr-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 10px;
    right: 10px;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #6366f1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .status-wait {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #16a34a;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .pix-input {
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #eef2ff;
    color: #4f46e5;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .btn-confirm {
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .payment-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
</style>

<body>

<%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>
<%- include('../partials/sidebar.ejs') %>

<main id="main" class="main" style="min-height: 85vh;">
<br/><br/>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-xl-10">

        <div class="card payment-card shadow-sm">
          <div class="card-body p-4">

            <div class="row g-4">

              <!-- LADO ESQUERDO -->
              <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3 class="payment-title mb-2">Pagamento PIX</h3>
                <p class="payment-subtitle mb-4">
                  Escaneie o código abaixo para ativar o <strong>FinanceFlow Pro</strong> instantaneamente.
                </p>

                <div class="qr-box">
                  <div class="qr-placeholder">
                    <i class="bi bi-qr-code"></i>
                    <div class="qr-badge">
                      <i class="bi bi-lightning-fill"></i>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <p class="fw-bold mb-1">Total a pagar: R$ 29,90</p>

                  <div class="status-wait mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-clock"></i>
                    AGUARDANDO PAGAMENTO...
                  </div>

                  <div class="mb-2 text-uppercase text-muted" style="font-size: 0.65rem;">
                    ou use o pix copia e cola
                  </div>

                  <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control pix-input bg-white"
                      value="00020126580014BR.GOV.BCB.PIX0136d88f..."
                      readonly>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">
                      <i class="bi bi-clipboard"></i>
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- LADO DIREITO -->
              <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">

                <div>
                  <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4">Próximos passos</h4>

                  <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div>Abra o app do seu banco preferido.</div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div>Selecione a opção de pagar via PIX / QR Code.</div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div>Após o pagamento, clique no botão abaixo para liberar seu acesso.</div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <a href="/dashboard/plano/index"
                     class="btn btn-primary btn-confirm w-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2">
                    Já realizei o pagamento
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                  </a>

                  <div class="payment-note">
                    O acesso é liberado automaticamente após a confirmação do banco,
                    geralmente em menos de 10 segundos.
                  </div>
                </div>

              </div>

            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
<%- include('../partials/script.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
